form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Attachment to form N-14 for N-648 Medical Exception, N-648

full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/13/2023 Attachment to form N-14 for N-648 Medical Exception A#: 90 414 260 We are unable to accept your N-648 at this time. Please return this letter and the N-648 to your doctor. Have the N-648 completed and bring it with you to the next interview. Please keep this appointment. Please do not mail or drop off the N-648. To the Physician: SHECKED JAN 2.9.1999 Please complete the N-648 with the following information and return to the applicant. Identify the applicant on the medical certification. Please complete and/or clarify the following on the existing Form N-648. Please attach a supplemental sheet to this form. Please, provide Dsm code and Dsm diagnosis Also, forwish Additional information The hen Alzhaimar_ stay medications, tests performed etc. thank you Please provide the Medical records pertaining to claimed disability or impairment. Provide an accurate assessment of the applicant's disability or impairment and how it prevents the applicant from learning the required English language, history and civics for Naturalization. Establish your qualifications to make this medical certification. Please provide a more legible N-648. N-648 was reviewed by; (SDAO)
